I have a rare brain disease called Trigeminal Neuralgia which is the most painful disease in the world and AKA "the S*****E pain", once I get affiliate on twitch I can begin getting donations to save up for my 7th brain surgery. I was in a near fatal wreck another driver caused and it severely damaged my entire neck and spine and the disease followed soon after. If you want to hear my full story you can check out either link if you would like to. Talking is the most painful thing to do so sometimes my talking is non existent or limited.

Here's the University of Texas' Trigeminal Neuralgia Research Center:
https://www.uthscsa.edu/patient-care/physicians/services/trigeminal-neuralgia

This is of the kind of unimaginable pain I'm in daily & have been for the past 7 years:
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trigeminal_neuralgia

First episode of Trigeminal Neuralgia AKA "The S****e Pain". NSFW, listen with headphones. Do not listen to around children. It's extremely hard to listen to:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkNsD-fdl3g

You can keep track of my progress on my new YouTube channel for frequent updates:
https://www.youtube.com/@XavierGoFundMeBrainSurgery
https://www.gofundme.com/f/curejrofthemostpainfuldiseaseintheworld
